---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NameGenerator from '../components/NameGenerator.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Pet Name Generator - Cute Dog, Cat & Animal Names"
  description="Generate thousands of cute, cool, and funny pet name ideas for puppies, kittens, dogs, cats, and birds. Filter by male, female, or neutral names."
  keywords="pet name generator, dog names, cat names, puppy names, kitten names, pet names, cute pet names, animal names"
>
  <div class="space-y-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header/Intro -->
    <div class="text-center space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#111111] dark:text-white leading-none">
        Pet Name Generator
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Find the perfect name for your new companion. From popular classics to unique foods, colors, and personalities, discover animal name ideas here.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Generator Component -->
    <NameGenerator category="pet" categoryName="Pet" />

    <!-- SEO Content Section -->
    <section class="border-t border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#222222] pt-10 mt-12 space-y-6 text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888] text-sm leading-relaxed theme-transition">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#111111] dark:text-white">How to Name Your New Pet</h2>
      <p>
        Bringing home a new pet is a joy. When choosing a name for your dog, cat, or other animal friend, consider these helpful guidelines:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Short is Sweet:</strong> Pets respond best to short names with one or two syllables (like <em>Max</em> or <em>Luna</em>). It is easier for them to recognize.</li>
        <li><strong>Test commands:</strong> Make sure the name doesn't sound too similar to common commands. For example, the name "Kit" sounds like "Sit", which could confuse a puppy.</li>
        <li><strong>Match their Personality:</strong> Spend a few days watching how they behave. An energetic kitten might suit <em>Storm</em> or <em>Ziggy</em>, while a sleepy puppy might be <em>Biscuit</em> or <em>Oreo</em>.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
